              code: "2_body_kit",
              display_name: "Body kit",
              description: "The body kit is unique because of the position of the assembly and the ability to remove the whole unit in one piece. It is constructed from Polypropylene (PP) and with Starks’ proprietary design to reduce the amount and thickness of plastic but still maintain strength and flexibility. There are three colors: Stark Red, Forest Gray and Snow White.\nThe fork covers aren't included in the body kit.",
