                {
                  code: "portabloe_charger_uk",
                  display_name: "Portable charger",
                  description: "Compact, Powerful, and Built for Adventure\nDimensions: 14.7 × 6.1 × 25 cm (5.79 × 2.4 × 9.8 in)\nWeight: 2.2 kg (4.8 lbs)\nCharging Capacity: 3.3 kW\nInlet Current: Max 16 A\nCharging Time (0 – 80 % @ 220 V): ~ 82 minutes\n\nNote - In the VARG MX 1.0 Gen 1, the cable is not long enough to reach the charging port when the portable charger is placed on the footpeg. The charger must be positioned higher.",
