                {
                  code: "fast_charger",
                  display_name: "Fast Charger 7 kW",
                  description: "Fast 7 kW charger with 32 A plug, delivering rapid power to fully charge the Stark VARG in just one hour. Please note that the charger requires 32 A for full capacity. \n\nRest of World plug; Use a standard socket compatible with  IEC 60309-2 32A 3P 230V 6h Blue color to connect the power supply. Ensure that the plug connection is reliable and that the device is reliably grounded. \n\nNote: This is a high power single-phase device (max. ~7.4 kW). Regulations may apply. Confirm compliance with your installer.\n",
